        <li><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-remove"></span> Style in all the Pages</li>
        <li><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-remove"></span> Load Log-in and Sign-up on Click</li>
        <li><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-remove"></span> Squirrel profile Picture</li>
        <li><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-remove"></span> A Squirrel can Add others</li>
        <li><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-remove"></span> The Squirrel can accept or deny it</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

